  <bioghist id="aspace_343ca973a48d868f572163be3596b00b">
    <head>ORGANIZATIONAL HISTORY</head>
<p>Moosewood Restaurant opened in Ithaca, NY in 1973. Moosewood, Inc. is a collectively owned business whose members share responsibilities and participate in the various jobs necessary to run what has grown from a very small natural foods restaurant to become a larger and more diversified company with a line of salad dressings, soups, and frozen main-dish entrees. With an emphasis on healthful natural foods cuisine, Moosewood has been acclaimed as a driving force in the world of creative vegetarian cooking.</p>  </bioghist>
  <scopecontent id="aspace_1c4df6b93d77fa1cd41604b0d7328be0">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Records of Moosewood, Inc., including menus from the restaurant and special events, work on cookbooks, files on publicity and public recognition, restaurant policies and management, photographs, and correspondence.</p>  </scopecontent>
